 group are NOT a walk in the park.<br /><br />On the subject of uh, roleplay.. when has this game ever really been about roleplay?<br /><br />"YOU hit a mob for 50 damage"?<br />All kinds of UIs on the screen?<br />"LOADING.. PLEASE WAIT" zonings?<br />NPCs and players having their names above their heads?<br /><br />This isn't a game designed specifically for roleplaying. <br />There is no reason that a group should or shouldn't get more experience for the same mob a soloer kills. <br />Why would there be?<br />It's all part of game balance, a steady amount of experience for the risk and time spent.<br /><br />I am honestly fairly happy with the changes to experience. I hate it that I get less soloing than before, but it's not <i>that</i> much, and grouping exp will go a lot faster now.<br /><br />Just my opinion on it.</span></font></td>
